description:
Danny is taking Everything Iconic back to the early aughts to celebrate the iconic era w/ Kristin Cavallari (The Hills/Laguna Beach & E!'s Very Cavallari), Daniel Franzese (Mean Girls), Ashley Parker Angel (O-Town & Broadway's Wicked), & Nikki Blonsky (Hairspray/Smash).

*For bonus episodes, join the Patreon at www.Patreon.com/EverythingIconic Web: www.EverythingIconic.com Twitter: www.Twitter.com/DannyPellegrino Facebook: www.Facebook.com/PellegrinoDanny Instagram: www.Instagram.com/DannyPellegrino
